claim.claim-text:
6. A disk drive, comprising: 
a base plate; 
a spindle motor mounted to said base plate; 
a disk that is rotated by said spindle motor to create a flow of air; 
an actuator arm mounted to said base plate; 
a transducer coupled to said actuator arm and said disk; and, 
an air deflector that is coupled to said base plate and extends over said disk.
